{"tid":367274,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［桌球］有無人識玩打硃仔","createTime":"2017-08-20T15:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T04:58:41.000Z","uid":57818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45b2e47a7b4938ad3f94068b452f074563bc2e4c","tid":367274,"uid":57818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"琴晚落波樓見人玩<br />\n覺得幾得意<br />\n自己都上網睇下啲玩法<br />\n但係無一個好完整既規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以問下大家 交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n譬如打10，20 <br />\n出統贏10 但自摸就位位20<br />\n咁一但多人玩咁自摸果位咪fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定還是每人5蚊會公平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋當打入左無人抽到既硃仔<br />\n應該拎番出黎打定由佢<br />\n如果拎番出黎又擺係邊"},{"pid":"1c37f4d0189fca44be99630e9306c216b676933d","tid":367274,"uid":56544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:57:31.000Z","msg":"最憎打珠仔班死mk<br />\n又嘈又食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5-6個人圍住張枱叫囂 阻住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5c4f8ce25301437019af861ef4820260e508e1","tid":367274,"uid":57818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最憎打珠仔班死mk<br />\n又嘈又食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5-6個人圍住張枱叫囂 阻住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你話又嘈又叫囂我覺得係睇人<br />\n但食煙就落得波樓就預左<br />\n就算你唔食 走果陣點都會成身煙味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8818b074dd6f36f11ccaa95ae37c290bbf162a","tid":367274,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琴晚落波樓見人玩<br />\n覺得幾得意<br />\n自己都上網睇下啲玩法<br />\n但係無一個好完整既規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以